title: SoKo - Not Sokute and Live Compilation
description:
SoKo - Not Sokute and Live Compilation

This is an mp3 + ogg compilation of SoKo&#039;s Not Sokute EP and her live performance on De Sorte Spejdere of DR P3 (Danish national radio).

Tracks:
01      SoKo    The Dandy Cowboys
02      SoKo    Shitty Day
03      SoKo    I&#039;ll Kill Her
04      SoKo    Take My Heart
05      SoKo    It&#039;s Raining Outside
06      SoKo    People Always Look Better In The Sun
07      SoKo    My Ex-Boyfriends
08      SoKo    Enemy
09      SoKo    Everybody&#039;s Seeking For Happiness
10      SoKo    Wet Dreams
11      SoKo    Souvenirs
12      SoKo    I&#039;ll Kill Her (DR P3 Live Version)

The first 5 tracks are taken from the "Soko - Not Sokute EP (2007)" torrent on TPB ( http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3683849/Soko_-_Not_Sokute_EP_(2007) ) and are kept in their original mp3 format.
The 7 remaining live tracks are cut out from from P3&#039;s De Sorte Spejdere&#039;s podcast ( http://podcast.dr.dk/p3/dss/2007/DSS080607.mp3 ), and has been amplified. These are compressed using ogg/vorbis quality 9,99 which is probably a waste due to the quality of the source, so it is not my fault the sound quality isn&#039;t any better, blame the recording and compression of the podcast.
